  "readme_html": "\n        \n          <p>This is an uncensored version of <a href=\"https://huggingface.co/Skywork/Skywork-o1-Open-Llama-3.1-8B\" rel=\"nofollow\">Skywork/Skywork-o1-Open-Llama-3.1-8B</a> created with abliteration (see <a href=\"https://github.com/Sumandora/remove-refusals-with-transformers\" rel=\"nofollow\">remove-refusals-with-transformers</a> to know more about it).<br>\nThis is a crude, proof-of-concept implementation to remove refusals from an LLM model without using TransformerLens.</p>\n\n<h3>References</h3>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://huggingface.co/huihui-ai/Skywork-o1-Open-Llama-3.1-8B-abliterated\" rel=\"nofollow\">HuggingFace</a></p>\n\n        \n      "
